data.description: This home is located in the Bay Oaks Subdivision in Irvington which has been a sought-after place to live for decades. This home features two stories and a very spacious open living room area that will be great for hosting friends and family. Kitchen has solid surface counter tops, recess lighting, and overlooks the living room.  Master bedroom has a tray ceiling with crown molding. Separate shower and tub, double vanity, and walk-in closet in the master bathroom. Large patio area in the backyard that is another great area for entertaining family and friends. It has a large yard and a storage building as well as a second story balcony. Call your favorite realtor to request a showing!
